Introduction

MSG Wannabe (Korean: MSG워너비; Japanese: MSGワナビー) is a project boy group formed through MBC's "Hangout with Yoo", hosted by Yoo Jae Suk. The group consists of Running Man Jee Seok Jin, singer-actor Kim Jungmin, KCM, Simon Dominic, Actors Lee Dong Hwi and Lee Sang Yi, Wonstein, and Parc Jae Jung. They made their official debut on July 3, 2021 through the music show "Music Core."
